  "ai_usage": "Use for real-estate, rentals, and marketplace browse pages. Provide a labeled filter bar (location/type/price), a featured listing, and a responsive grid of property <article> cards with photo, price, address, beds/baths/area as text, and a save toggle (aria-pressed). Recolor via --accent; replace listings. Keep controls labeled and focus-visible; consider a map split-view variant.",
  "path": "effects/website-templates/real-estate-listing.html",
  "source": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\" />\n<title>Real Estate Listings</title>\n<script type=\"application/json\" id=\"effect-meta\">\n{\n  \"id\": \"real-estate-listing\",\n  \"title\": \"Real Estate Listings\",\n  \"summary\": \"A property search page: a filter bar, a featured listing, and a responsive grid of property cards with price, beds/baths/area, and a save toggle.\",\n  \"description\": \"The core real-estate browse experience — a sticky search/filter bar (location, type, price), one large featured listing, and a grid of property cards each showing a photo area, price, address, key stats, and a heart-to-save button. Clean and trustworthy.\",\n  \"theme\": \"website-templates\",\n  \"categories\": [\"template\", \"real-estate\", \"listing\"],\n  \"tags\": [\"real-estate\", \"listings\", \"property\", \"filters\", \"cards\", \"full-page\"],\n  \"tech\": [\"html\", \"css\", \"js\"],\n  \"era\": \"2020s\",\n  \"difficulty\": \"intermediate\",\n  \"dependencies\": [],\n  \"browser_support\": \"All modern browsers (CSS Grid).\",\n  \"performance_notes\": \"Card hover lifts + save toggles + reveals. Gradient placeholders for photos. No libraries.\",\n  \"accessibility_notes\": \"Filter controls are labeled; cards are articles with real links; the save button is a toggle with aria-pressed and a naming label; key stats are text. Focus-visible throughout.\",\n  \"customization\": [\n    { \"name\": \"--accent\", \"description\": \"Brand + price color\", \"default\": \"#0e7c66\" },\n    { \"name\": \"listings\", \"description\": \"Card data (price, address, stats)\", \"default\": \"edit markup\" }\n  ],\n  \"variations\": [\"Add a map split-view\", \"Sort dropdown (price/newest)\", \"Mortgage estimate per card\"],\n  \"related\": [\"ecommerce-product\", \"luxe-serif\", \"card-lift\"],\n  \"ai_usage\": \"Use for real-estate, rentals, and marketplace browse pages. Provide a labeled filter bar (location/type/price), a featured listing, and a responsive grid of property <article> cards with photo, price, address, beds/baths/area as text, and a save toggle (aria-pressed). Recolor via --accent; replace listings. Keep controls labeled and focus-visible; consider a map split-view variant.\"\n}\n</script>\n<style>\n  :root{--bg:#f6f7f5;--surface:#fff;--ink:#19211d;--muted:#67726c;--line:#e4e8e4;--accent:#0e7c66;--gold:#c08a2d;--r:16px;}\n  *{box-sizing:border-box}html{scroll-behavior:smooth}\n  body{margin:0;background:var(--bg);color:var(--ink);font-family:\"Inter\",system-ui,sans-serif;line-height:1.6}\n  a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none}\n  .wrap{max-width:1140px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 1.4rem}\n  nav{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;height:68px}\n  .brand{font-weight:800;font-size:1.15rem;color:var(--accent)}\n  .links{display:flex;gap:1.4rem;color:var(--muted);font-size:.92rem;align-items:center}.links a:hover{color:var(--ink)}\n  .btn{background:var(--accent);color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:10px;padding:.6rem 1.1rem;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer}\n  .head{padding:1.5rem 0 .5rem}.head h1{font-size:clamp(1.8rem,4vw,2.6rem);font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-.02em;margin:0 0 .3rem}\n  .head p{color:var(--muted);margin:0}\n  .filters{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:10;background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:14px;\n    display:grid;grid-template-columns:2fr 1fr 1fr auto;gap:.7rem;padding:.7rem;margin:1.2rem 0;box-shadow:0 6px 20px rgba(20,40,30,.06)}\n  .filters input,.filters select{border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:10px;padding:.6rem .8rem;font:inherit;background:var(--bg);color:var(--ink)}\n  .filters input:focus,.filters select:focus{outline:none;border-color:var(--accent);box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(14,124,102,.18)}\n  .featured{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.4fr 1fr;gap:0;border-radius:var(--r);overflow:hidden;border:1px solid var(--line);background:var(--surface);margin-bottom:1.6rem}\n  .featured .ph{aspect-ratio:16/10;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0e7c66,#7bbf8a);position:relative}\n  .featured .tag{position:absolute;top:1rem;left:1rem;background:var(--gold);color:#fff;font-size:.74rem;font-weight:800;padding:.3rem .7rem;border-radius:999px}\n  .featured .body{padding:1.8rem;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center}\n  .price{color:var(--accent);font-weight:800;font-size:1.8rem}\n  .addr{color:var(--muted)}\n  .stats{display:flex;gap:1.2rem;margin:1rem 0;color:var(--muted);font-size:.92rem}\n  .stats b{color:var(--ink)}\n  .grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1.2rem;padding-bottom:2rem}\n  .card{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:var(--r);overflow:hidden;transition:transform .18s,box-shadow .18s}\n  .card:hover{transform:translateY(-5px);box-shadow:0 18px 40px rgba(20,40,30,.12)}\n  .card .ph{aspect-ratio:4/3;position:relative}\n  .c1{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#7bbf8a,#0e7c66)}.c2{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#d0a44c,#a06a1f)}.c3{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#6aa9d6,#2c6b99)}\n  .c4{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#c98b8b,#8a4b4b)}.c5{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#9b8fd6,#5a4b99)}.c6{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#86c0b5,#3a7a6c)}\n  .save{position:absolute;top:.7rem;right:.7rem;width:38px;height:38px;border-radius:50%;border:none;background:rgba(255,255,255,.9);cursor:pointer;font-size:1.05rem;display:grid;place-items:center}\n  .save[aria-pressed=\"true\"]{color:#e0294e}\n  .card .body{padding:1rem 1.1rem}\n  .card .price{font-size:1.3rem}.card h3{margin:.1rem 0;font-size:1rem}.card .addr{font-size:.85rem}\n  .card .stats{font-size:.82rem;margin:.7rem 0 0;gap:.9rem}\n  .btn:focus-visible,.save:focus-visible,.card a:focus-visible{outline:3px solid var(--gold);outline-offset:2px}\n  footer{border-top:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--muted);text-align:center;padding:2.2rem 0;font-size:.9rem}\n  .reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px);transition:opacity .6s,transform .6s ease}.reveal.in{opacity:1;transform:none}\n  @media(max-width:860px){.featured{grid-template-columns:1fr}.grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}.filters{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}.links a:not(.btn){display:none}}\n  @media(max-width:560px){.grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.filters{grid-template-columns:1fr}}\n  @media(prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){.card{transition:none}.reveal{opacity:1;transform:none;transition:none}html{scroll-behavior:auto}}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"wrap\">\n    <nav><div class=\"brand\">⌂ Haven</div><div class=\"links\"><a href=\"#\">Buy</a><a href=\"#\">Rent</a><a href=\"#\">Sell</a><a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\">List a property</a></div></nav>\n\n    <header class=\"head\"><h1>Homes in Riverdale</h1><p>248 listings · updated today</p></header>\n\n    <form class=\"filters\" aria-label=\"Filter listings\">\n      <input type=\"search\" placeholder=\"City, neighborhood, or ZIP\" aria-label=\"Location\" value=\"Riverdale\" />\n      <select aria-label=\"Property type\"><option>Any type</option><option>House</option><option>Condo</option><option>Townhouse</option></select>\n      <select aria-label=\"Price range\"><option>Any price</option><option>Up to $500k</option><option>$500k–$1M</option><option>$1M+</option></select>\n      <button class=\"btn\" type=\"submit\">Search</button>\n    </form>\n\n    <article class=\"featured reveal\">\n      <div class=\"ph\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Featured property photo\"><span class=\"tag\">★ Featured</span><button class=\"save\" aria-pressed=\"false\" aria-label=\"Save featured listing\">♥</button></div>\n      <div class=\"body\">\n        <div class=\"price\">$1,240,000</div>\n        <h2 style=\"margin:.2rem 0;font-size:1.4rem\">Cedar Hill Modern</h2>\n        <div class=\"addr\">128 Cedar Hill Rd, Riverdale</div>\n        <div class=\"stats\"><span><b>4</b> beds</span><span><b>3</b> baths</span><span><b>2,850</b> sqft</span><span><b>0.4</b> ac</span></div>\n        <p style=\"color:var(--muted);margin:.2rem 0 1rem\">Light-filled architectural home with floor-to-ceiling glass, a chef's kitchen, and a private garden.</p>\n        <a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\" style=\"align-self:flex-start\">View details →</a>\n      </div>\n    </article>\n\n    <div class=\"grid\">\n      <article class=\"card reveal\"><div class=\"ph c1\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Property photo\"><button class=\"save\" aria-pressed=\"false\" aria-label=\"Save 22 Birch Lane\">♥</button></div><div class=\"body\"><div class=\"price\">$685,000</div><h3>22 Birch Lane</h3><div class=\"addr\">Riverdale</div><div class=\"stats\"><span><b>3</b> bd</span><span><b>2</b> ba</span><span><b>1,640</b> sqft</span></div></div></article>\n      <article class=\"card reveal\"><div class=\"ph c2\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Property photo\"><button class=\"save\" aria-pressed=\"false\" aria-label=\"Save 9 Maple Court\">♥</button></div><div class=\"body\"><div class=\"price\">$899,000</div><h3>9 Maple Court</h3><div class=\"addr\">Riverdale</div><div class=\"stats\"><span><b>4</b> bd</span><span><b>3</b> ba</span><span><b>2,210</b> sqft</span></div></div></article>\n      <article class=\"card reveal\"><div class=\"ph c3\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Property photo\"><button class=\"save\" aria-pressed=\"false\" aria-label=\"Save 410 River St\">♥</button></div><div class=\"body\"><div class=\"price\">$475,000</div><h3>410 River St #12</h3><div class=\"addr\">Riverdale</div><div class=\"stats\"><span><b>2</b> bd</span><span><b>2</b> ba</span><span><b>1,080</b> sqft</span></div></div></article>\n      <article class=\"card reveal\"><div class=\"ph c4\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Property photo\"><button class=\"save\" aria-pressed=\"false\" aria-label=\"Save 77 Oakridge Dr\">♥</button></div><div class=\"body\"><div class=\"price\">$1,050,000</div><h3>77 Oakridge Dr</h3><div class=\"addr\">Riverdale</div><div class=\"stats\"><span><b>5</b> bd</span><span><b>4</b> ba</span><span><b>3,100</b> sqft</span></div></div></article>\n      <article class=\"card reveal\"><div class=\"ph c5\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Property photo\"><button class=\"save\" aria-pressed=\"false\" aria-label=\"Save 3 Willow Way\">♥</button></div><div class=\"body\"><div class=\"price\">$540,000</div><h3>3 Willow Way</h3><div class=\"addr\">Riverdale</div><div class=\"stats\"><span><b>3</b> bd</span><span><b>2</b> ba</span><span><b>1,520</b> sqft</span></div></div></article>\n      <article class=\"card reveal\"><div class=\"ph c6\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Property photo\"><button class=\"save\" aria-pressed=\"false\" aria-label=\"Save 215 Elm Terrace\">♥</button></div><div class=\"body\"><div class=\"price\">$760,000</div><h3>215 Elm Terrace</h3><div class=\"addr\">Riverdale</div><div class=\"stats\"><span><b>4</b> bd</span><span><b>2</b> ba</span><span><b>1,980</b> sqft</span></div></div></article>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>© <span id=\"yr\"></span> Haven Realty · Equal Housing Opportunity</footer>\n  </div>\n  <script>\n    document.getElementById('yr').textContent=new Date().getFullYear();\n    document.querySelectorAll('.save').forEach(function(b){b.addEventListener('click',function(e){e.preventDefault();var on=b.getAttribute('aria-pressed')!=='true';b.setAttribute('aria-pressed',on);});});\n    var io=new IntersectionObserver(function(es){es.forEach(function(e){if(e.isIntersecting){e.target.classList.add('in');io.unobserve(e.target)}})},{threshold:.1});\n    document.querySelectorAll('.reveal').forEach(function(el){io.observe(el)});\n  </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"
}
